---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Ghana Scenario Analysis: Multiple Futures, Honest Probabilities"
  description="Scenario-based analysis of Ghana's economy. Multiple possible futures with probability estimates, indicator watchlists, and audience-specific implications."
  keywords="Ghana economic scenarios, Ghana economy forecast 2026, Ghana policy scenarios, Ghana investment risk scenarios"
>
  <div class="hero hero--bg hero--scenarios">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-label">Multiple Futures</div>
      <h1>Scenario Analysis</h1>
      <p>3-5 possible futures with probability estimates. Observable indicators. What breaks the thesis. Updated each cycle.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="section reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-label">Published</div>
        <div class="section-title">Scenarios</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-grid">
        <a href="/scenarios/triple-shock-2026" class="article-card">
          <span class="card-tag scenario">Scenario Analysis</span>
          <h3>Ghana's Triple Shock: Three Scenarios for 2026</h3>
          <p>Hormuz, cocoa, and the GSE crashed simultaneously. Four scenarios: managed absorption (45%), quick resolution (15%), compound stress (25%), and cascading failure (10%).</p>
          <div class="card-meta"><span>March 29, 2026</span><span>Macro Scenario</span><span>15 min read</span></div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
